data.description: Price Improvement!THIS 80 ACRES CAN BE SUBDIVEDED, YOU CAN HAVE 2 HOMES/WATER WELLS HERE! NO HOA! Bring your toys and trailers! PRIVACY! NEW solar system! NEW roof! NEW plumbing throughout this home! NEW HVAC system! NEW carpet! NEW tankless hot water tank! NEW re-piped 8 person hot tub included! 40 FT Connex box included. Gas stove and gas fireplace. Skylights bringing tons of natural light. Newer Windows! Grand 4 piece master bath. Walk In Closets! HUGE room sizes. Decks on either side of home for grilling and entertainment. XLARGE mud room space of front door entrance, STORAGE! Chicken coops have electric. Electric and water to the horse barn. 2 car detached workshop!
